{"tid":1558001,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【良心港姐】譚小環「助養」抗爭者","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T11:28:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5879d564a377918f6d7cfe2971a4e93538027f6","tid":1558001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190910/20765262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F20765262&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4a3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=bee76eaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F20765262&h=735055c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190910/20765262</a><br />\n<br />\n【良心港姐】譚小環「助養」抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568037290_2a3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568037290_2a3f.jpg&h=f8fae225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1994年冠軍 譚小環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港小姐由無綫選出，對外言論一向要謹慎，但有不少良心港姐都會為抗爭者發聲，暗中或表明支持逆權運動，甚至不理被封殺影響前途。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃嘉雯尷尬唔認做第三者<br />\n<br />\n1994年冠軍 譚小環<br />\n譚小環與老公蔡強榮多次表態支持反送中，兩人開設的小食店「渣哥」早前為支持抗爭者，更加入「助養」行列，幫抗爭者醫肚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568037287_8081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568037287_8081.jpg&h=7149d4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2005年五強 袁彌明<br />\n袁彌明多次親身出來遊行支持反送中外，也發聲抨擊警方濫權，旗下彌明生活百貨的十間專門店上月響應8.5大罷工，暫停營業一天。<br />\n相關新聞：楊詠彤爆樽打前男友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568037287_fa30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568037287_fa30.jpg&h=43a851ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012年十強 林泳淘<br />\n《東張西望》主播林泳淘，有傳因3月底在Ig呼籲參加第一次反修例遊行被雪藏，6月才解封，但7月時又貼出拿着寶礦力的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568037288_f1c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568037288_f1c2.jpg&h=edbb449a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2015年冠軍 麥明詩<br />\n麥明詩當選後被發現曾現身支持佔中，今年6月9日103萬人遊行，她暗撐：「有啲目標聽落好似好荒謬，一班人齊心就乜都有可能！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568037289_9d3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568037289_9d3a.jpg&h=2dad4ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年冠軍 馮盈盈<br />\n馮盈盈當選後被爆於2014年雨傘運動期間，在網上以粗口批評政府。今年6月她在Ig貼出燭光照，悼念從太古廣場墮下的梁凌杰。 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n楊詠彤爆樽打前男友<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n趙詠瑤撐師妹築人鏈<br />\n<br />\n黃嘉雯尷尬唔認做第三者<br />\n楊詠彤爆樽打前男友<br />\n趙詠瑤撐師妹築人鏈<br />\n陶傑支持港人 王晶鬧：賤種<br />\n港姐決賽首輪即Out3號梁敏巧黃絲身份 遭無綫落閘"},{"pid":"b493a92afd953b8e5573ca9c081de67a0c14c794","tid":1558001,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係港姐"},{"pid":"98ccf25bd3f046553e3288ef8a6cc7945c7976ca","tid":1558001,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rmbo1S6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmbo1S6.jpg&h=520d5fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣哥d凍奶茶係幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，隔幾日就啪一支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"1326a8369ee68bb03f61e7fa6229c923befc43d1","tid":1558001,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"港姐"},{"pid":"13d287bd170a96ec24b46ecdc59582c2b99f4506","tid":1558001,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98ccf25bd3f046553e3288ef8a6cc7945c7976ca","tid":1558001,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rmbo1S6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmbo1S6.jpg&h=520d5fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣哥d凍奶茶係幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，隔幾日就啪一支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"Wa我秀"},{"pid":"8e81945b1ad37af4d875d5c180f847391c709d8f","tid":1558001,"uid":223615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"袁彌明反共反左好多年"}]}